TopicTitle: Complete Mission (4x Speed) Launch Rover to Find Face on Duna in Kerbal Multi Player

Articles.Content: I made a rover, launched it from the KSC and sent it to Duna. Aerobraked at Duna and after an orbit, the rover descended to the planet's surface. A few atmospheric path-finding burns set the rover near the face, while a final rocket-parachute combo guided the rover down for a pinpoint landing! KMP Area 51-2 Server
